The box measure 6 X 3 X 2.5 and can easily hold 600 address cards.

This set includes:
1 bamboo box
12 dividers with letter tabs {measures 3x2.5 inches}
600 inserts cards {measures 3x2.5 inches}
~~~average business card measures 2.5 X 3 inches~~~

{all of the paper is hand-cut by me}

Everything in it's place. Store all of the business cards you've collected and all of your family & friends info in one place. 
